        "body":  "Codex review: NEEDS_CORRECTION\n\nFinding 1 (source-doc stale after modifying the extracted tests): `crates/editor-egui-host/src/menu_tests.rs:8-14` still frames the file as the behavior-identical extraction from #301 with \"same tests.\" That was true when `menu_tests.rs` was created, but this PR intentionally changes the equality tests and adds the accelerator-display test, so the live module doc now overstates the current file state. Please reword that paragraph to preserve the historical extraction note without claiming the current file still contains the same tests (for example: extraction kept the module path/visibility the same at the time; this file now also carries the menu shortcut-display coverage).\n\nI did not find a functional issue in the shortcut-display implementation. The File/Edit accelerator strings match the live key-routing sources, Play/View are correctly left `None`, the render helper is display-only, and the split-exemption is mechanically justified by the current `lib.rs` line count. CI was still running when I reviewed.\r\n",
